'''霍華德·格雷沙姆·霍金斯'''（{{lang-en|Howard Gresham Hawkins}}；{{bd|1952年|12月8日}}），是[[美國|美國]][[紐約州|紐約州]]出身的[[工會|工會]]活动家和[[行動主義|環境活動家]]，亦是[[美國綠黨|美國綠黨]]的聯合創立人。他獲綠黨提名{{le|霍伊·霍金斯2020年美國總統競選活動|Howie Hawkins 2020 presidential campaign|參選}}[[2020年美國總統選舉|2020年美國總統選舉]]，其主要競選綱領包括制定[[生態社會主義|生態社會主義]]綠色新政策，在2010年首次提出；以及建立一個可行、獨立的工人階級政治和社會運動，並反對民主黨、共和黨與一般的資本主義<ref name="IndependentPolitics2006">{{cite book |last1=Hawkins |first1=Howie |title=Independent politics : the Green Party strategy debate |url=https://archive.org/details/independentpolit00hawk |date=April 11, 2006 |publisher=Haymarket Books |isbn=9781931859301 }}</ref>。

自1960年代起，霍金斯在{{le|和平退伍軍人|Veterans for Peace|反戰}}<ref name="VetsForPeace2016">{{cite news |title=U.S. Vets Lead Civil Disobedience Action at Crestwood to Protest Seneca Lake Gas Storage |url=https://www.veteransforpeace.org/who-we-are/member-highlights/2016/01/27/us-vets-lead-civil-disobedience-action-crestwood-protest-sen |accessdate=16 March 2020 |work=www.veteransforpeace.org |date=27 January 2016 |language=en |archive-date=2020-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421061814/https://www.veteransforpeace.org/who-we-are/member-highlights/2016/01/27/us-vets-lead-civil-disobedience-action-crestwood-protest-sen |dead-url=no }}</ref>、{{le|蛤殼同盟|Clamshell Alliance|反核}}<ref name="NYT2018">{{cite news |last1=McKinley |first1=Jesse |title=0-for-23: An Undeterred Green Party Candidate on His Long Losing Streak |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/10/19/nyregion/howie-hawkins-green-party-governor.html |accessdate=16 March 2020 |work=The New York Times |date=19 October 2018 |archive-date=2020-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725230009/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/10/19/nyregion/howie-hawkins-green-party-governor.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>和工人運動中發揮了領導作用；他也是一位退休的{{le|國際貨車司機兄弟會|International Brotherhood of Teamsters|貨車司機}}和建築工人，從2001年到2017年退休前在都在[[联合包裹服务|UPS]]夜班負責卡車卸貨<ref>{{cite news |last1=Baker |first1=Chris |title=Syracuse's Howie Hawkins mulls a run for president |url=https://www.syracuse.com/politics/2019/04/syracuses-howie-hawkins-mulls-a-run-for-president-with-green-party.html |accessdate=16 March 2020 |work=syracuse |date=3 April 2019 |language=en |archive-date=2020-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626103149/https://www.syracuse.com/politics/2019/04/syracuses-howie-hawkins-mulls-a-run-for-president-with-green-party.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="EugeneWeekly">{{cite news |title=It Ain't Easy Being Green |url=https://www.eugeneweekly.com/2020/01/09/it-aint-easy-being-green/ |accessdate=16 March 2020 |work=Eugene Weekly |date=9 January 2020 |archive-date=2020-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714115907/https://eugeneweekly.com/2020/01/09/it-aint-easy-being-green/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

霍金斯曾二十四次競選各種職務，包括2006年代表{{le|紐約州綠黨|Green Party of New York}}參選{{le|2006年紐約州美國參議院議員選舉|United States Senate election in New York, 1998|參議院}}；{{le|2010年紐約州長選舉|2010 New York gubernatorial election|2010年}}、{{le|2014年紐約州長選舉|2014 New York gubernatorial election|2014年}}、{{le|2018年紐約州長選舉|2018 New York gubernatorial election|2018年}}和代表綠黨參選紐約州長；{{le|2017年錫拉丘茲市長選舉|2017 Syracuse mayoral election|2017年}}參選錫拉丘茲市長，但均告失敗<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.syracuse.com/politics/2020/06/syracuses-howie-hawkins-secures-green-party-nomination-for-president.html |title=Syracuse’s Howie Hawkins secures Green Party nomination for president |accessdate=2020-09-01 |archive-date=2020-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813054429/https://www.syracuse.com/politics/2020/06/syracuses-howie-hawkins-secures-green-party-nomination-for-president.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

